    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road? I\u2019m parting with my car, and it has been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really wonderful shape and has been well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. It runs smoothly and is ready for its next big adventure. Come by and take it for a test drive, I think you'll love it!",
