    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS actuation. This example is a driver-focused machine, boasting a Getrag six-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential that remains tight. The chassis has been proactively addressed with rear subframe reinforcement plates, ensuring structural integrity under high lateral loads. Suspension geometry is maintained via refreshed bushings and Bilstein monotube dampers, providing excellent turn-in response. While the aesthetic reflects its tenure on the road, the mechanical vitals\u2014including valve clearances and rod bearing health\u2014are within spec, making this an ideal candidate for the enthusiast who prioritizes drivetrain precision and atmospheric performance over a garage-queen pedigree.",
      "price": 34500.0,
