    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic balance of performance and value, having been maintained with a focus on longevity and reliability. The exterior finish retains a high-gloss shine, though closer inspection reveals the minor, expected road wear consistent with a car that has been enjoyed. The body panels are straight, and the alloy wheels are in great shape. Inside, the cabin remains a refined space; the premium upholstery shows only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster, and the dashboard remains free of any cracks or sun damage. All electronic features, including the infotainment system, dual-zone climate control, and power-adjustable seating, operate perfectly. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs smoothly, benefiting from a documented history of oil changes and preventative maintenance. The brakes are firm, and the suspension provides a composed ride without any unusual noises. This is a solid, dependable vehicle that is ready for daily commutes or long-distance touring without hesitation.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
